headline: UnitedHealth Is Approaching a Pivotal Moment. Should Investors Buy the Stock Before July 29?
summary: Disappointing second-quarter results from Elevance Health might not bode well for UnitedHealth Group.  UnitedHealth Group could calm investors with new full-year guidance and details on how it will return to growth.  It's been an awful, horrible, lousy year so far for UnitedHealth Group (NYSE: UNH).
